{"tid":956654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「行走骷髏」3年內變真人春麗！她走出霸凌鍛鍊肌肉，嚇壞惡霸同儕","createTime":"2018-12-26T12:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T03:49:27.000Z","uid":212399,"like":7,"dislike":74,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b4838d5ab191ef483d892c5df0be69ddbc278cc8","tid":956654,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T12:09:29.000Z","msg":"霸凌事件層出不窮，校園裡，經常發生同儕排擠、共同嘲笑的行為。今天文內這位少女，名為艾米莉，她也曾是遭受霸凌的可憐孩子，但是她走出來了，如今還是衛冕三次的健美冠軍呢！<br />\n11歲時，艾米莉身材較豐腴，腰圍和雙腿胖胖的，當時，她總是淪為被同學排擠、嘲笑的對象，「大胖豬」、「胖妹」、「死肥豬」這些惡言經常讓她回家後向父母哭訴、傷心不已。<br />\n為了不再被同學嘲笑，艾米莉開始拒絕吃飯，她不僅拒吃三餐，也不再碰零食、甜飲，過度沉浸在「節食減肥」的方式中，後來，艾米莉反而得了厭食症，且精神不濟，她經常自行催吐、一看到食物就嘔吐，甚至有一陣子，艾米莉每天只吃一顆蘋果，讓自己保持「不餓到昏倒」即可的程度。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3486/3486241.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3486%2F3486241.jpg&h=b486bd0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n後來，艾米莉遇到改變她一生的健身老師萊納多，萊納多不僅傳授艾米莉吃不胖的健康飲食方法，也開始教她鍛鍊身材、變壯，艾米莉發現，萊納多的方法確實能讓她變得更健康，又能變得精壯，因此逐漸不再厭食，且漸漸變得開朗。<br />\n在萊納多的引導下，艾米莉踏進健美行業，她熱愛健身、鍛鍊肌肉線條，她永遠謹記萊納多說的，「你必須好好吃飯，否則永遠沒有足夠的體力練出更棒的身材，我也將不再指導你！你要保持身心健康才行。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3486/3486246.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3486%2F3486246.jpg&h=be43b417&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3486/3486245.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3486%2F3486245.jpg&h=30ccb3f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n後來，艾米莉不僅恢復正常飲食，體重也恢復到正常標準，更拿下三次健美冠軍頭銜，現在，她身上的肌肉曲線，讓許多男性都相當羨慕，當年那些霸凌她、欺負她的小惡霸同儕，看到艾米莉的現況後，也都嚇壞了！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3486/3486243.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3486%2F3486243.jpg&h=f6a3ba73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不敢相信眼前這位真人版春麗是當年忽胖忽瘦的同學。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3486/3486247.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3486%2F3486247.jpg&h=72e9b489&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/37735\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F37735&d=PU72c7fMpcCXWV7VN8abOv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=532c5d0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/37735</a>"},{"pid":"33571a2d297f14b923be71e2550460981c5e9b6b","tid":956654,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T12:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa6b743e7ee3f3785a172f83f4557c76556edcc7","tid":956654,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T12:12:26.000Z","msg":"我大隻啲"},{"pid":"5ab6d7a538a6bc10df4fe7fdb8f420c6606464bc","tid":956654,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T12:12:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瘦左好正"},{"pid":"1fd1ec11c40c6751e10b631202cf366860183613","tid":956654,"uid":53687,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T14:18:17.000Z","msg":"個編輯真係無SEARCH過春麗個比例係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ecbbbdfbf1c98126239b705c3d6011b4a98eb8c","tid":956654,"uid":118120,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T14:40:19.000Z","msg":"點解要咁極端一係極瘦一係極肌肉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32612fc15b12bb76158ee9ab74735a6ddb29bc3e","tid":956654,"uid":7903,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7ecbbbdfbf1c98126239b705c3d6011b4a98eb8c","tid":956654,"uid":118120,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T14:40:19.000Z","msg":"點解要咁極端一係極瘦一係極肌肉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"r